### Skills Demonstrated

Conducted a customer base audit using Microsoft Excel to analyze a dataset of 41 transactions. Applied frequency distribution techniques to classify price data into six equal-width intervals, computing relative and cumulative frequencies. Constructed a histogram to identify distribution shape and dominant customer segments. Interpreted a positively skewed price distribution and formulated evidence-based managerial recommendations, including targeted upselling strategies for the $200–$299 core segment. Demonstrated proficiency in Excel data organization, COUNTIF formulas, and chart creation using the Analysis ToolPak.
